title: Warmia Cup is back again!
feed: Eduarda Santos Lisboa and Ana Patricia Ramos of Brazil are the new champions of the world! On Sunday, Duda and Ana Patricia, Youth Olympic champions at Nanjing 2014, completed a winning run of eight consecutive victories to claim the women’s final at the Beach Volleyball World Championships Rome 2022.
